  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Underground_GM_Finale
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - Breath and Flesh, both yours now. The Guardian does not give its Fragment lightly, and neither do I give my praise.
  - You are no longer an apprentice. From this moment you are an Adept, and the deeper workings of alchemy are open to you.
  - One realm remains. Beyond the Underground lie the Ruins, where the Fragment of Soul is kept. It is the hardest trial of all, and many never return from it.
  - Gather your strength, then climb to the Ruins. I will meet you where the old world ended.
